283  void UpdateChannels(icUInt16Number nNumChannels) {
284  m_nLastNumChannels = nNumChannels;
285  if (nNumChannels>m_nMaxChannels)
286  m_nMaxChannels=nNumChannels;
287  }
288 
289  bool Begin();
290 
291  icUInt16Number GetMaxChannels() { return m_nMaxChannels; }

293  icFloatNumber *GetDstBuf() { return m_pixelBuf2; }
294 
295  void Switch() { icFloatNumber *tmp; tmp=m_pixelBuf2; m_pixelBuf2=m_pixelBuf1; m_pixelBuf1=tmp; }

298
